---

<section
  id="informacion"
  class="py-20 bg-[#107A58] min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center relative"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start mb-12 md:mb-16 gap-8"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-medium text-white tracking-tight max-w-2xl leading-tight"
      >
        Inversión inteligente: Tranquilidad y Plusvalía.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-md font-light leading-relaxed">
        Propiedad saneada en Ciudad de Dios, estratégicamente ubicada cerca a
        servicios esenciales y con fácil acceso a la ciudad.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
      <!-- Left Column: Stats Grid (Occupies 5 columns) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Stat Card 1 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-center h-full min-h-[180px]"
        >
          <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2"
            >Título</span
          >
          <span class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Independizado en Sunarp</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat Card 2 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-center h-full min-h-[180px]"
        >
          <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2"
            >3</span
          >
          <span class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Cuadras de la Panamericana</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat Card 3 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-center h-full min-h-[180px]"
        >
          <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2"
            >200m²</span
          >
          <span class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Área total del terreno</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat Card 4 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-center h-full min-h-[180px]"
        >
          <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2"
            >100%</span
          >
          <span class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Servicios (Agua/Luz)</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Feature Card (Occupies 7 columns) -->
      <div
        class="lg:col-span-7 bg-white rounded-3xl p-4 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start flex-1 gap-6">
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Disfruta de la tranquilidad de una zona residencial con calles
            asfaltadas, rodeada de áreas verdes y conectada a todo lo que
            necesitas para vivir cómodamente.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/M9XF%2BXV5,+Arequipa+04016/@-16.298869,-71.6266963,3a,49y,72.17h,85.37t/data=!3m8!1e1!3m6!1slGlxsxhKA_XkP8EPb1XooA!2e0!5s20250101T000000!6shttps:%2F%2Fstreetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com%2Fv1%2Fthumbnail%3Fcb_client%3Dmaps_sv.tactile%26w%3D900%26h%3D600%26pitch%3D4.632107799496495%26panoid%3DlGlxsxhKA_XkP8EPb1XooA%26yaw%3D72.17385047543584!7i16384!8i8192!4m15!1m8!3m7!1s0x91423a3c814e348b:0x90b04e61a65e847b!2sYura!3b1!8m2!3d-16.2520984!4d-71.6836503!16s%2Fg%2F11c5g_wgyv!3m5!1s0x9142370b5a7ab4df:0x59b0889f1a78a738!8m2!3d-16.2999714!4d-71.6252692!16s%2Fg%2F11j37d1hkr?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDEyNS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="bg-[#107A58] cursor-pointer text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-[#0e6b4d] transition-colors inline-block text-center"
          >
            Ver ubicación
          </a>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-full md:w-1/2 h-64 md:h-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden relative"
        >
          <img
            src="/image1.png"
            alt="Modern house with pool"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes bounce-in-up {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    60% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  section {
    animation: bounce-in-up 1s ease-out forwards;
  }
</style>
